### Project endpoints
# GET routes are public. POST/PUT/DELETE may require a JWT depending on whether
# authMiddleware is enabled on these routes.
# Requires the VS Code "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client).

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

# Paste a JWT from the verify-otp response here to authenticate write requests.
@token = PASTE_JWT_HERE

# Set after creating a project (copy the "_id" from the create response).
@projectId = PASTE_PROJECT_ID_HERE

### List all projects (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects

### Get a single project by id (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}

### Create a project
# "image" is the URL returned by POST /api/upload (see upload.rest).
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "My Portfolio Site",
  "category": "Web",
  "year": "2026",
  "link": "https://example.com",
  "image": "https://res.cloudinary.com/your-cloud/image/upload/sample.jpg"
}

### Update a project
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "category": "Web",
  "year": "2026",
  "link": "https://example.com",
  "image": "https://res.cloudinary.com/your-cloud/image/upload/sample.jpg"
}

### Delete a project
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
